WEBVTT

00:04:28.679 --> 00:04:30.917
of "because they're volunteers."

00:04:31.274 --> 00:04:32.545
Late night calls?

00:04:32.569 --> 00:04:35.449
Yes, because they're volunteers
and have day jobs.

00:04:35.473 --> 00:04:38.926
Business trips that are almost
exclusively only on weekends?

00:04:38.950 --> 00:04:41.740
Yes, because they're volunteers
and have day jobs.

00:04:42.309 --> 00:04:43.768
Not to pat myself on the back,

00:04:43.792 --> 00:04:45.578
but I got quite good at my job.

00:04:45.602 --> 00:04:48.178
I was thriving off of
the relationships I was building.

00:04:48.601 --> 00:04:52.436
And the best way I knew how to judge
whether I had earned someone's trust

00:04:52.460 --> 00:04:54.787
was if they would come
and ask me for help.

00:04:54.811 --> 00:04:56.006
I loved it.

00:04:56.030 --> 00:04:57.744
Every time we did year-end retreats

00:04:57.768 --> 00:05:00.484
and we talked about what we wanted
to be in the next year,